@NODE 5. "English Manual"
There is NO english manual.

This manual is only for personal documentation purposes. I don't
believe that anyone will use this program, because there are a lot
of objects included in Jongl and we didn't get one object from the
users of Jongl.
So if you are interested to design objects, write to me, and I will
try to provide you the information you need.
@ENDNODE
